more sophisticated sound hardware...

975
01:02:18,301 --> 01:02:20,326
...and they came up
with a different sound...

976
01:02:20,536 --> 01:02:21,969
...that I wasn't involved with.

977
01:02:23,206 --> 01:02:26,232
