978
01:02:26,442 --> 01:02:28,637
...how horrible
the one on the Mac II was.

979
01:02:28,845 --> 01:02:32,246
So a tritone is the most dissonant sound
you could imagine.

980
01:02:32,448 --> 01:02:34,814
And stack four of them together.

981
01:02:36,586 --> 01:02:40,283
And that was the sound that you heard
when you turned on the Mac.

982
01:02:40,490 --> 01:02:43,357
Which was horrible. And so...

983
01:02:44,494 --> 01:02:48,021
